vernac_cmds: Inductive inmonoid (X : Ensf) : Word -> Prop := | inmonoid_nil : inmonoid X nil | inmonoid_cons : forall (w : Word) (e : Elt), inmonoid X w -> dans e X -> inmonoid X (cons e w).
Fixpoint Inmonoid (X : Ensf) (w : Word) {struct w} : Prop := match w with | nil => True | cons a w' => dans a X /\ Inmonoid X w' end.
Lemma i_I : forall (X : Ensf) (w : Word), inmonoid X w -> Inmonoid X w.
red in |- *; simpl in |- *; exact I.
change (dans e X /\ Inmonoid X w0) in |- *.
Lemma I_i : forall (X : Ensf) (w : Word), Inmonoid X w -> inmonoid X w.
cut (dans x X /\ Inmonoid X w0); auto.
intro H1; elim H1; clear H1.
Lemma inmonoid_cons_inv : forall (X : Ensf) (w : Word) (a : Elt), inmonoid X (cons a w) -> inmonoid X w.
cut (dans a X /\ Inmonoid X w); auto.
intro H1; elim H1; clear H1.
Lemma inmonoid_cons_inv2 : forall (X : Ensf) (a : Elt) (w : Word), inmonoid X (cons a w) -> dans a X.
cut (dans a X /\ Inmonoid X w); auto.
intro H1; elim H1; clear H1.
Lemma inmonoid_inclus : forall (E F : Ensf) (x : Word), inclus E F -> inmonoid E x -> inmonoid F x.
intros E F x inclus_E_F inmonoid_E_x.
intros w e inmonoid_E_w inmonoid_F_w dans_e_E.
apply inmonoid_cons; [ assumption | apply inclus_E_F; assumption ].
Fixpoint Append (w1 : Word) : Word -> Word := fun w2 : Word => match w1 with | nil => w2 | cons a w3 => cons a (Append w3 w2) end.
Lemma Append_w_nil : forall w : Word, Append w nil = w :>Word.
replace (Append (cons x w0) nil) with (cons x (Append w0 nil)); auto.

Inductive append : Word -> Word -> Word -> Prop := | append_nil : forall w : Word, append nil w w | append_cons : forall (w1 w2 w3 : Word) (a : Elt), append w1 w2 w3 -> append (cons a w1) w2 (cons a w3).
Lemma Append_inmonoid_g : forall (X : Ensf) (w1 w2 : Word), inmonoid X (Append w1 w2) -> inmonoid X w1.
replace (Append (cons x w) w2) with (cons x (Append w w2)); auto.
apply inmonoid_cons_inv2 with (Append w w2); auto.
Lemma Append_inmonoid_d : forall (X : Ensf) (w1 w2 : Word), inmonoid X (Append w1 w2) -> inmonoid X w2.
replace (Append (cons x w) w2) with (cons x (Append w w2)); auto.
Lemma inmonoid_Append : forall (X : Ensf) (w1 w2 : Word), inmonoid X w1 -> inmonoid X w2 -> inmonoid X (Append w1 w2).
intros x w H w2 H0 H1.
replace (Append (cons x w) w2) with (cons x (Append w w2)); auto.
Definition eqwordset (l1 l2 : wordset) : Prop := forall w : Word, (l1 w -> l2 w) /\ (l2 w -> l1 w).
Lemma eqwordset_refl : forall L : wordset, eqwordset L L.
Lemma eqwordset_sym : forall l1 l2 : wordset, eqwordset l1 l2 -> eqwordset l2 l1.
elim (H w); clear H; intros; auto.
Lemma eqwordset_trans : forall l1 l2 l3 : wordset, eqwordset l1 l2 -> eqwordset l2 l3 -> eqwordset l1 l3.
Definition islanguage (X : Ensf) (L : wordset) : Prop := forall w : Word, L w -> inmonoid X w.
Fixpoint Word_ext (f : Elt -> Elt) (w : Word) {struct w} : Word := match w with | nil => nil | cons a w' => cons (f a) (Word_ext f w') end.
Lemma inmonoid_map : forall (f : Elt -> Elt) (a : Ensf) (w : Word), inmonoid a w -> inmonoid (map f a) (Word_ext f w).
elim H; [ unfold Word_ext in |- *; auto | idtac ].
intros; unfold Word_ext in |- *; simpl in |- *.
apply inmonoid_cons; try apply dans_map_inv; auto.
Lemma cons_cons : forall (x1 x2 : Elt) (w1 w2 : Word), x1 = x2 :>Elt -> w1 = w2 :>Word -> cons x1 w1 = cons x2 w2 :>Word.
Definition fun_consaw_a (w : Word) : Elt := match w return Elt with | nil => zero | cons a w' => a end.
Definition fun_consaw_w (w : Word) : Word := match w return Word with | nil => nil | cons a w' => w' end.
Lemma cons_cons_inv : forall (x1 x2 : Elt) (w1 w2 : Word), cons x1 w1 = cons x2 w2 -> x1 = x2 /\ w1 = w2.
replace x1 with (fun_consaw_a (cons x1 w1)); auto.
replace x2 with (fun_consaw_a (cons x2 w2)); auto.
replace w1 with (fun_consaw_w (cons x1 w1)); auto.
replace w2 with (fun_consaw_w (cons x2 w2)); auto.
Lemma cons_cons_inv1 : forall (x1 x2 : Elt) (w1 w2 : Word), cons x1 w1 = cons x2 w2 :>Word -> x1 = x2 :>Elt.
cut (x1 = x2 :>Elt /\ w1 = w2 :>Word); [ intuition | auto ].
Lemma cons_cons_inv2 : forall (x1 x2 : Elt) (w1 w2 : Word), cons x1 w1 = cons x2 w2 -> w1 = w2.
cut (x1 = x2 /\ w1 = w2); [ intuition | auto ].
Lemma nil_or_cons : forall w : Word, w = nil \/ (exists x : Elt, (exists w0 : Word, w = cons x w0)).
